entries.title_d: Since the destruction of their leader, the Cloak forces have been scattered. Some remnant forces have regrouped in the Dathomir system, and could be plotting a return. You must get to the Dathomir system and destroy these Cloak remnants.
entries.title: Corellia System: Destroy Cloak Remnants Duty
entries.targets_detected: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: <\#pcontrast3  Enemy craft approaching on attack vector.\#pcontrast1 >
entries.targets_behind: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: <\#pcontrast3  Enemy craft approaching from the rear.\#pcontrast1 >
entries.quest_location_d: The Cloak remnants seem to have regrouped in the Dathomir system.
entries.quest_destroy_d: Destroy all Cloak remnants that you find. When you have eliminated an entire attack wing, your computer will update the navigation waypoint to the next area of activity.
entries.level_increase: Cloak activity in this system is increasing due to your presence.
entries.level_boss_dead: Good work, pilot. Cloak activity in this area seems to have diminished. Stand by.
entries.level_boss: \#pcontrast1 CorSec Command: <\#pcontrast3  Cloak vessel communication is increasing. It seems they are sending an officer after you.\#pcontrast1  >
entries.found_loc: Transmitting location of most recent Cloak activity. Proceed to this location and destroy all targets.
entries.complete: Good work, pilot. No further Cloak activity is detected in this system. Return to the station for debriefing.
entries.boss_detected: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: <\#pcontrast3  Cloak Officer signature detected. Enemy craft incoming.\#pcontrast1 >
